  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deductive logic puzzles with a colorful twist!</h2> <br>Enjoy handmade and procedurally generated cross-stitch puzzles that will keep you thinking in different ways. With a weave and some colorful thread, can you complete a pattern with only clues of which colors go in each row and column? Later on, stubborn thread will be thrown in that can only be stitched in certain spots!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/1a8eb02201cc5b141dd2619ed7b3109e.avif?t=1670860578\" width=523 height=523 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/cd51c7f83127c69b9a197d5f241c900c.webp?t=1670860578\" width=48 height=48 /></span> 40 handmade, thematic puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/99b06a610e7b66552b3830b1fb7235de.webp?t=1670860578\" width=48 height=48 /></span> 5 handmade puzzles every week (if connected to internet)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/54f6cce553152925efd86caf43142d3b.webp?t=1670860578\" width=48 height=48 /></span> 8 endless game modes of procedurally generated puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/4f880f669ba88965efe394e8f4f1507a.webp?t=1670860578\" width=48 height=48 /></span> Cross-stitch generator that works with uploaded JPG or PNG images<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188220/extras/cd51c7f83127c69b9a197d5f241c900c.webp?t=1670860578\" width=48 height=48 /></span> Download cross-stitches and share via code",
